Articles.Content:
My game crashes every time I try to run 0.90.0 on my Windows 7 PC. I have 8 GB RAM, a Nvidia GTX 750ti, and a AMD 6 core processor.

I've tried running in the "AMD compatibility mode" but that did not fix the issue.

A message pops up and says "The game crashed. The crash report folder name "2015-02-14_193652 next to game executable. It would be great if you'd send it to the developer of the game!".

I took a look in the crash report and it said something about Unity screwing up. Here's the log when it runs into the problem:
